data.description:
Well-maintained 2 bedroom, 2 bath home with 1491 square feet.  The home features an open living room, kitchen, dining area, beautiful laminate tiles, walk-in closets, and a master bath with double vanities and a large walk in shower. The back yard is landscaped and private with a comfortable sitting area to relax and enjoy with family and friends. The exterior is all masonry and hardy plank for very low maintenance, composition roof, in-ground sprinkler system, solar panels, and fenced backyard.  This home is in a well desired area of Lampasas and wont last long. 
Come look today!
